{"tid":349132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[IT wake up]陳茂波 花逾十萬元請人搞網誌同Facebook！","createTime":"2017-08-06T10:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T05:18:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c506802777383f8c9fdaed8d72de4aecfff88eaa","tid":349132,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:07:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170806/00176_066.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170806%2F00176_066.html&d=qmBGhWIfcDOk6vQx21bcvDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=e1fc0ae4\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170806/00176_066.html</a><br />\n<br />\n新一屆政府行政會議成員、金融管理局前總裁任志剛（任總）日前撰文批評政府喺過去十年一直採取「守財奴」政策，搞到政府庫房水浸，但就拖經濟後腿。雖然成篇文章都冇點名批評邊個，但擺明就係針對掌管香港庫房十年嘅前財政司司長曾俊華（鬍鬚曾）。眼見鬍鬚曾備受批評，現任財政司司長陳茂波（波叔）可能都感覺到壓力，所以就決定唔做守財奴，仲豪花逾十萬元請人搞網誌同Facebook（Fb）。不過搞網誌同Fb都每月使逾十萬元，咁樣用公帑法，唔通佢唔怕畀人話佢大花筒？"},{"pid":"74b64f65e3b7b76d9e1b707eb76fe5e32cc717d0","tid":349132,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d756cf3892e129cf6e152da3c9740989fd5781","tid":349132,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:14:32.000Z","msg":"點解唔係$0.5/post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d53b736ef56eb2aaf38c8fb2fce873d3098890","tid":349132,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> it=high pay"},{"pid":"3951af9f6249bc4bfc1ddcafb88b59a8324a0dfd","tid":349132,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:32:39.000Z","msg":"又再次證明IT好有市場"},{"pid":"746e8d8d67053521295baf46764da74f556d862b","tid":349132,"uid":56432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T10:37:01.000